{"tid":240414,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"10週年版iPhone8傳新配色　「玫瑰金邊+瓷白身」（有相）","createTime":"2017-05-12T11:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T02:33:34.000Z","uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a35baf46779f756c86c6ac40d8c00790c677692","tid":240414,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"Apple 自從在 Tim Cook 當上 CEO 後，iPhone 產品線不再只有黑跟白兩色。近年每一代新推出型號都有新色上場，像是香檳金、玫瑰金、亮黑、Product Red 等。來到今年的十週年版本 iPhone 8，現時也有消息指出將會加入新配色。到底這個新配色是怎樣呢？近期很紅的爆料達人 Benjamin Geskin 已經為我們帶來了渲染設計圖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/C_TghNSXgAAUVf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FC_TghNSXgAAUVf9.jpg&h=02f74291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBenjamin Geskin 近日在 Twitter 上傳了多張有關 iPhone 8 新配色的 3D 渲染圖，據消息指出新加入的新配色是「玫瑰金+白」，這跟現時已經有的玫瑰金色有點不同。原因在於 iPhone 8 的機身設計預計是改用底面玻璃設計，再配以不銹鋼金屬邊框整合而成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/C_fWfjJXUAAkS9M.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FC_fWfjJXUAAkS9M.jpeg&h=99b4c74b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c6a51eb0e6854fe16faa2338b18644be6e08fd0","tid":240414,"uid":10635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"曲邊mon 會唔會假左d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848479d5150e6054f8c499bfbf5c667c48ceffa1","tid":240414,"uid":67490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:53:32.000Z","msg":"老實講如果用藍邊會好睇啲"},{"pid":"3c33b50d6c4883232d14eac1af4a436e17f35be2","tid":240414,"uid":3500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"隻色好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df093e2b691700f9621daa9121bec8f554e8297c","tid":240414,"uid":36822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply